Plucene-Plugin-Analyzer-SnowballAnalyzer
========================================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Plucene
  Lingua::Stem::Snowball

